Notes / small ops checklist
	•	Enable Blob Versioning on the container so overwrites keep history (no code changes needed).
	•	Keep your filenames strictly lowercase and underscore-separated to match the resolver.
	•	If you need a different language fallback (e.g., zh → en), extend langFallback or read from config.
	•	Error handling:
	•	TemplateNotFoundException → treat as configuration/content issue (log + stop or DLQ).
	•	StorageAccessException → transient I/O (your caller can retry).
	•	TemplateParseException → bad JSON content (log + fix the blob).

If you want the resolver to also return blob ETag / Last-Modified for telemetry, I can add those fields in TemplateDocument—just say the word.